OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783756130
OL,3,CKing meets grandchildren Archie and
OL,4,CLilibet for first time in four years
OL,6,FThe King has been reunited with his
OL,7,Fgrandchildren after the Duke and
OL,8,FDuchess of Sussex visited the head of
OL,9,Fstate at his country home, it is
OL,10,Funderstood.
OL,12,FCharles welcomed Meghan and Harry's
OL,13,Fchildren to his Highgrove residence
OL,14,Fduring the afternoon after days of
OL,15,Fspeculation over whether the family
OL,16,Fmeeting would take place.
OL,18,FArchie, seven, and Lilibet, five, last
OL,19,Fsaw their grandfather in person during
OL,20,FQueen Elizabeth II's Platinum Jubilee
OL,21,Fcelebrations in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
