OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783756130
OL,3,CKing meets grandchildren Archie and
OL,4,CLilibet for first time in four years
OL,6,FIt is understood the Queen who has a
OL,7,Fprivate home near to the King's
OL,8,FGloucestershire property was also
OL,9,Famong the group.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe meeting between Charles and the
OL,17,Fyoung prince and princess is likely to
OL,18,Fbe interpreted as a sign of the
OL,19,Fthawing of the relationship between
OL,20,Fthe King and his son Harry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
