OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783756130
OL,3,CKing meets grandchildren Archie and
OL,4,CLilibet for first time in four years
OL,6,FThe pair were estranged for some time
OL,7,Fespecially after Harry criticised his
OL,8,Ffather, stepmother Camilla, brother
OL,9,Fthe Prince of Wales and sister-in-law
OL,10,FKate in his Oprah interview, Netflix
OL,11,Fdocumentary, interviews and his
OL,12,Fautobiography Spare, after stepping
OL,13,Fdown from the working monarchy six
OL,14,Fyears ago.
OL,16,FHis rift with William is ongoing and
OL,17,Fshows no sign of abating and the
OL,18,Ffamily reunion took place during the
OL,19,Fsame afternoon William was playing in
OL,20,Fa charity polo match at Windsor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
