OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783756130
OL,3,CKing meets grandchildren Archie and
OL,4,CLilibet for first time in four years
OL,6,FIn February 2024 Harry made a
OL,7,Ftransatlantic dash from his
OL,8,FCalifornian home to Britain to see his
OL,9,Ffather following his cancer diagnosis,
OL,10,Fwhich may have led to the first steps
OL,11,Fin a reconciliation between the pair.
OL,13,FHarry had planned to bring his family
OL,14,Fto the UK while he undertook a week-
OL,15,Flong series of events promoting
OL,16,Fcharities and organisations close to
OL,17,Fhis heart including the Invictus Games
OL,18,Fhe founded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
